97
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:18,000
and D has to be positive-- it's a negative number.

98
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:22,110
Therefore, it will always be a global maximum--

99
00:04:22,110 --> 00:04:24,610
because this will always be less than zero.

100
00:04:24,610 --> 00:04:28,950
So all I'm going to do now is solve for this Qg.

101
00:04:28,950 --> 00:04:31,190
