00:04:31,190 --> 00:04:33,960
I'm just rearranging here, and I get to this--

103
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:37,260
the Q* is going to be equal to this relationship.

104
00:04:37,260 --> 00:04:41,040
And cleaning up a little bit, I get it down to this form.

105
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:43,860
